Pronunciation[edit]

  • (Classical) IPA(key): /komˈpel.loː/, [kɔmˈpɛl.lʲoː]
  • (Ecclesiastical) IPA(key): /komˈpel.lo/, [kɔmˈpɛl.lɔ]

Verb[edit]

conpellō (present infinitive conpellāre, perfect active conpellāvī, supine conpellātum); first conjugation

  1. Alternative form of compellō
